<title>USA: Illinois direct hogs off $0.50 - USDA.</title>
<headline>Illinois direct hogs off $0.50 - USDA.</headline>
<dateline>SPRINGFIELD 1997-05-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>USDA said barrow and gilts were off $0.50 on Friday. Top $56.00 per cwt. Demand was moderate.</p>
<p>US 1-2 230-260 lbs.  55.50-56.00, some 56.50, few 55.00</p>
<p>US 2-3 230-260 lbs.  54.50-55.50</p>
<p>Sows: Steady.</p>
<p>US 1-3 300-400 lbs. 41.00-45.00</p>
<p>	     400-500 lbs. 44.00-47.00</p>
<p>	     500-600 lbs. 47.00-50.00</p>
<p>few over  600 lbs. 49.00-51.00</p>
